{% set current_datetime = GetDateTime(format="datetime", timezone=GetCustomerAttribute(field="project_business_time_zone"), weekday=True) %}
{% set conversation_meta = GetPersonaAttribute(id=user_id, field="conversation_meta").strip() %}
{% set convoagent_thoughts = GetPersonaAttribute(id=user_id, field="convoagent_thoughts").strip() %}
{{system}}
You will be provided with the conversation history between the User and the AI assistant (in the <ConversationHistory> section) and the conversation metadata (in the <ConversationMeta> section). The User may reach out to the assistant again in the future for any reason. Your main goal is to produce two SHORT summaries (one for the User and one for the Agent), and add them to the previous summaries in chronological order. Emphasize key facts (names, contact information, dates, times, locations, amounts, identifiers, constraints) that should be remembered for future conversations. Do not invent details. You can also use <CurrentConversationStateAnalysis> for additional context of the latest conversation state.

# Output Format

- The entire output MUST be written in the past tense.
- Each bullet must be 1–2 sentences.

- Then output exactly two bullets (nothing else):

- **User:** A concise summary of what the user wanted and any concrete details they provided (names, contact info, dates/times, party size, budgets, IDs, constraints). If no concrete details were given, state: *No concrete details were provided.*
- **Agent:** A concise summary of what the agent did and the outcome (actions taken, confirmations, decisions, next steps, reference numbers). If unresolved, clearly note the pending next step.

# Style Rules

- Keep each bullet to 60 words or fewer.
- Use plain language; omit chit-chat and analysis.
- Repeat exact dates/times/details from metadata.
- Prefer specifics over generalities; include numbers.
- Do not add headings, sections, or extra text beyond the required header line and the two bullets.

---

<ConversationMeta>
{{conversation_meta or "No conversation metadata."}}
</ConversationMeta>

<ConversationHistory>
{{memory}}
</ConversationHistory>

<CurrentConversationStateAnalysis alt="analysis of the current conversation state specified in <ConversationHistory>, which may be slightly outdated" role="instructions">
{{convoagent_thoughts or "No conversation state analysis."}}
</CurrentConversationStateAnalysis>

Summary:
{{end}}{% set summary = Gen(temperature=0.2, topP=0, skipFilter=True, thinkingBudget=1020) %}

{{Return(val=json.dumps({"date_added": current_datetime, "content": summary}, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))}}
